item.description:
Are you thinking about dating again…….do you have reservations about on-line dating…….are you wondering where all the good ones have gone…….or what to do to actually meet them?

Meet relationship coach Deborah King and get some answers to your dating questions.

Deborah has worked for one of the top private on-line dating services and has spent the bulk of her life researching relationships and why some work and some don’t.

At the end of the night one lucky participant will win an hour long consult.


From Melody - I met my awesome hubby online so I am proof that it CAN work!  ha ha!  :)
item.name: For the Singles in Our Group! - Relationship Expert and Online Dating Q&A
